      "text": "みなさん、これがパワハラですよ！\nしかもこんな公の場で！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "isn't it~? Everyone‚ this is workplace bullying!\nAnd in a public place like this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
