      "text": "それじゃあみなさん、来年も私達リズノワを\nどうぞよろしくお願いしま～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ everyone‚ please continue to\nsupport LizNoir‚ next year too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
