      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ good job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん！　お疲れ様です～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san! Thank you so much~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "見ててくれましたか？\nこころの素晴らしいパフォーマンスを！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you see?\nKokoro's awesome performance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんだ。また一段と成長したなって思ったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I did. I thought you've grown even more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "そうでしょう、そうでしょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew it‚ I knew it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん不在という逆境で見事にセンターを\n務め上げる……はぁ～、自分の才能が恐ろしいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excellently taking on the center position\ndespite Rio-san's absence… My talent is amazing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "でも……やっぱりリズノワは四人が一番ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… LizNoir is at its best when the four of us are together‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "だって……莉央さんが駆け付けた時の安心感と、四人で\nパフォーマンスした時の一体感といったら、もう……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because… the sense of security when Rio-san arrives and\nthe unity when we perform together is just…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、見てて下さい！\n来年こそリズノワがトップを獲りますよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ please keep watching!\nNext year‚ LizNoir will definitely reach the top~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！　莉央さん！？\nいつから話を聞いてたんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?! Rio-san?!\nHow long have you been listening to us?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "今のは違うんです！　ああ、いや\nこの気持ちは嘘じゃないんですけど～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not what it sounded like! Oh‚ no…\nThese feelings are genuine‚ though~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "うわわ、葵さんに愛ちゃんまで！\nも～、その生温かい笑顔はなんなんですか～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no‚ Aoi-san and Ai-chan too!\nGeez‚ what's with those warm smiles~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年明けから数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later afte the new year",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 113.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
