      "text": "ふう、こっちの作業はひと段落ついたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew‚ this work is almost over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5033.333333300007,
          "startTime": 119.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "どうも～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、こころ？　どうしたんだ？\n今日は一日オフだっただろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ Kokoro? What's up?\nToday was supposed to be your day off‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですけど～\nリズノワでオフなのは私だけじゃないですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true‚\nbut isn't LizNoir on break today too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "仕事の兼ね合いでそうなったんだが……年末年始は\n忙しかったんだし、ゆっくりしていいんだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It turned out this way due to work overlap…You've been busy since\nthe end of the year‚ so it's okay to take it easy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
